data.description: *BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER *  A wonderful blend of modern design. Enjoy a stylish kitchen with SS appliances and granite countertops of this 4-bedroom 2 1/2 bath home. Stay cozy with dual zone HVAC and a smart thermostat. Benefit from a 2-car garage, spacious primary bedroom with walk-in closet, and a luxurious ensuite featuring a large walk-in shower. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, I-64, and Naval Station Norfolk. Experience an open floorplan with clear sightlines, making this home a true gem. Don't miss out – schedule a viewing today!  Property to be sold AS IS. Seller to make NO repairs.
